{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "本章介绍了两位主角：郭大路与王动。郭大路是一个大方马虎、武功高强却穷困潦倒的游侠，他做过镖师、厨子、卖唱、卖艺，甚至想做强盗，但每次都因过于大方或脾气不好而失败。王动是富贵山庄的庄主，懒得出奇却深藏不露，两人在富贵山庄相遇，郭大路用剑换来酒肉与王动分享，两人一见如故，成为朋友。本章展现了郭大路善良大方、不拘小节的性格，以及王动懒散却重情义的特点，为后续故事埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大路",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大江东去",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中原镖局",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳兄弟",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锦背低头花装弩",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_zhen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "罗振翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像郭兄如此高的身手，为什么不做镖头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_zhen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "罗振翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路也问：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么武功高的人要去保镖！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中原镖局",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我们却身无一技之长，叫我们去做什么呢？不做强盗，只怕一家人都得饿死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "做做小生意也好呀，就算卖馒头，也总比做强盗好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连一文本钱都没有，能做什么生意？不如现在就死了算了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有本钱，这容易，我有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "每人一百两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位恩公不但是大英雄、大豪杰，而且简直是个活菩萨、大圣人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路心里也是热血沸腾，感慨不已：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人之初，性本善，若非被逼得无路可走，又有谁愿意做强盗呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这匹马是二百八十两买来的，身上还剩下七百多两银子，加起来也有一千多两了。先赔他们再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剩下的呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剩下的镖局先垫上，我用副总镖头的薪饷慢慢来还。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你救过我，我替你赔镖银，就算还了债。像郭大爷你这样的人，我以前实在没有见到过，只求以后也莫要遇见才好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明天，又是另外一天了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "急征厨师。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你吃过糖醋鱼没有？你吃过鱼没有？糖醋鱼本来就不能做得太咸的，你知不知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天下的厨子若都像你这么凶，哪还有人敢上馆子？到了这种地步，别人就算还敢留他，他自己也呆不下去了。干了三天厨子，惟一的收获就是身上多了层油烟，口袋还是空的。但是，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此处不留人，自有留人处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大爷今天想吃点什么？喝点什么？今天小店的鱼是特地从江南快马捎来的，要不要活杀一条来配三十年陈的绍兴酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像郭大路这么样有气派的人，店小二不去巴结他去巴结谁？郭大路的脸却已红得像是喝过三十斤绍兴酒了，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是来卖唱的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这句话他怎么还能说得出口？过了大半天，他才结巴的说了句：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我来找人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉，原来一个人相貌长得太好，有时也很吃亏的，也许我长得丑些反而好些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路虽然是在叹着气，却几乎忍不住立刻要去照照镜子。卖唱也卖不成，干什么呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老天给了我这么样一双灵巧的手，我总有事可做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个落难的少年英雄，潦倒得在街头卖艺，恰巧遇着上一位老英雄和他娇媚的小女儿，对这落魄英雄的武功大为倾倒……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对，卖艺，就在街头卖艺，凭我这身武功，还怕没有人赏识？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不说也没关系，反正别人是来看我的本事，不是来听我说话的，只要我本事一拿出来，还怕人不围过来看么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "于是郭大路挽了挽袖子，掖了掖衣角，就在这街角上将他生平最得意的一套拳法练了起来。只见他拳起时如猛虎出柙，脚踢时如蛟龙入海，拳影翻飞，拳风虎虎，当真是每一招都有真才学，每一式都有真功夫。但别人非但没有围过来，反而都远远的避开了，就算有几个胆子大的，也只敢站在屋角偷偷地瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人忽然在街上打起拳来，莫非有了毛病？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我练的是真功夫，一点花拳绣腿都没有，这些凡夫俗子当然看不出好处来。好，我就再练点惊人的给他们瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想到这里，郭大路突然一个鹞子现身，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算要做贼，也得做大强盗，绝不能做偷鸡摸狗的小偷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "做贼也并不太坏，有很多劫富济贫的义盗，他们的故事岂非也一样能在江湖中流芳千古么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "于是郭大路决定做强盗，当然是做个义盗、大盗。这次他决定只许成功，不许失败。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要做好一件事，还未开始时，就一定先得计划周密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "找到什么值钱的东西没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就知道你找不到的，我已经找了三天，连最后一个破铁锅都被我拿去换烧饼了。你若还能找到别的，那本事真不小。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他长得本不算难看，只不过显得面黄肌瘦，连说话都是有气无力的样子，的确像是已饿了好几天。但他睡的这张床，却不折不扣是张好床。这空房子里怎么还会有这么样的一张好床？这人睡在床上干什么？郭大路忍不住问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里究竟是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说起这地方，可真是大大有名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有名？有什么名？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你听见过富贵山庄这名字没有？这里就是富贵山庄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "富贵山庄？这见鬼的地方居然叫富贵山庄？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点也不错，胖子既然可能变得很瘦，富贵山庄也可能变得很穷，这又有什么好稀奇的呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，你又是何许人也？呆在这种鬼地方干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不呆在这里呆在哪里？我就是富贵山庄第七代的庄主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路又怔住了。这人的眼睛一直盯着他手里的剑，忽又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这把剑看来倒不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本来就不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来总还值好几两银子吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好几两？你识货不识货？告诉你，这柄剑是我花一百多两银子买来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人的眼睛里好像有了光，说话的声音也响了，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你从这里下山，往左走，有家利源当铺，那里的朝奉虽然是个刮皮鬼，倒还很识货，你乘他们还没有打烊，赶快去，这柄剑至少还可以当二十两银子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他咽了口口水，接着又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当铺的斜对面，就是家老广开的烧腊店，做的烧鸭和脆皮肉都不错，隔邻还有酒卖。你当来银子后，就先买两只烧鸭、五斤肉、十斤酒，赶快送回来，我已经饿得很了，而且烧鸭冷了也不好吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路瞪大了眼睛，瞧着这人，那表情简直就和罗振翼在听他说话的时候一样。过了很久，他才吐出口气，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你叫我去把自己的剑当了，买酒肉回来送给你吃？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你总算听懂了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道我到这里来，是想来干什么的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当然知道，你是想来抢钱的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然知道我是强盗，还想在我身上打主意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你虽是强盗，我却是穷鬼，强盗遇见穷鬼，也只有自认晦气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路瞧着他，忽然发觉这人笑得很可爱，甚至很妩媚。他自己也忍不住笑了，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算你想在我身上打主意，至少也该自己把我这柄剑拿去当，自己去买酒回来给我吃才对呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要做好人就做到底，还是你走一趟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？你连动都懒得动？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想，我若是不懒，又怎么会穷成这样子呢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路第三次怔住了。他以前实在也没见过这样的人，他实在也拿这人没法子。他居然真的将剑换了酒肉回来。一条鸭腿、半斤酒下了肚，这人才从床上坐了起来，笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我吃了你的酒，却连你的名字都不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大路道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫郭大路，大方的大，上路的路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 503,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大路——你这人倒真的名副其实，真的很大路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？你叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 507,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫王动，帝王的王，动如脱兔的动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你实在应该叫做王不动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 511,
      "line_end": 513
    }
